name: Syra Agent
description: Syra is an innovative AI-powered trading ecosystem engineered to simplify and enhance cryptocurrency trading for its users. The project's core purpose is to democratize access to high-quality market signals and insights by automating the "hard work" of complex market analysis through an intelligent AI Agent. The platform's primary function is to generate and deliver real-time, actionable trading signals for various crypto assets. This service is accessible through two intuitive interfaces: a rapid-response Telegram Bot and a comprehensive Web App.
